      • getHostmask

        @NonNull
public String getHostmask()
        The full hostmask of the user in extban:user!login@hostname format. If there's no extban prefix extban: is not returned. If there's no login nor hostmask, meaning this is a service or the IRCd server "user", just the nick is returned
